<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<mei xmlns="http://www.music-encoding.org/ns/mei" meiversion="5.0">
  <meiHead>
    <fileDesc>
      <titleStmt>
        <title>It Came Upon A Midnight Clear</title>
        <title type="subtitle">Harp Arrangement — SSAATTBB + Pedal</title>
      </titleStmt>
      <pubStmt>
        <date isodate="2026-04-12" />
      </pubStmt>
    </fileDesc>
  </meiHead>
  <music>
    <body>
      <mdiv>
        <score>
          <!-- Key: Bb major (2 flats: Bb, Eb). All Bb→accid.ges="f", Eb→accid.ges="f" -->
          <!-- Meter: 6/8, L:1/4. In 6/8 with L=1/4: one beat = dotted quarter (3 eighths = 1.5 quarter).-->
          <!-- Two beats per bar (strong beat 1, weak beat 2), each a dotted quarter. -->
          <!-- L=1/4 means quarter=1 unit. 6/8 bar = 3 quarter units total (3/2 in quarters, or 6 eighths). -->
          <!-- In MEI meter.count=6 meter.unit=8. tstamp 1 = beat 1, tstamp 2 = beat 2 (starts at beat 1+3eighth=1.5 qtr). -->
          <!-- Wait — ABC L:1/4 with M:6/8: 6 eighth-note slots. F/2 = 1 eighth, F = 1 quarter (2 eighths), F3/2 = dotted quarter (3 eighths). -->
          <!-- So in MEI: dur="4" = quarter (2 eighth slots), dur="4" dots="1" = 3 eighth slots, dur="8" = 1 eighth slot. -->
          <!-- 6/8 bar total = 6 eighth slots. tstamp: beat 1 on eighth 1, beat 1.33 on eighth 2, beat 1.67 on eighth 3, beat 2 on eighth 4 etc. -->
          <!-- MEI tstamp in 6/8 with meter.unit=8: tstamp="1"=beat1, tstamp="2"=beat2 (halfway), tstamp="1.5"=mid-beat1... -->
          <!-- Using meter.count=6 meter.unit=8. tstamp="1" = downbeat, tstamp="4" = second group of 3 (beat 2). -->
          <!--
            PICKUP: F/2 = 1 eighth = F4
            M1 (6 eighths): d(4) A/2(8) c/2(8) B/2(8) Eb/2(8) — wait the ABC is: d A/2 "^Cm7"c/2 B/2 "^Eb"G/2
            Actually: d=quarter(2 eighths), A/2=eighth(1 eighth), c/2=eighth, B/2=eighth, G/2=eighth → total 6 eighths ✓
            Chords: beat1=Bb(I), beat1.5=Cm7(ii7) at the A/2, beat2=Eb(IV) at G/2?
            Actually reading: "^Bb"F/2 (pickup) | d A/2 "^Cm7"c/2 B/2 "^Eb"G/2 |
            M1: Bb for d+A/2, Cm7 for c/2+B/2, Eb for G/2? — that would be 2+1+1+1 = wrong sum
            Let me re-read: d=2, A/2=1, [then Cm7 annotation] c/2=1, B/2=1, [Eb annotation] G/2=1 → 6 ✓
            So: Bb for beat1 (d+A/2 = 3 eighths = dotted quarter), Cm7 for c/2+B/2 (2 eighths), Eb for G/2 (1 eighth)? — awkward
            Musically: treat as Bb for first 3 eighths (dotted quarter 1), Cm7 for next 2, Eb pickup to next bar.
            Actually simpler: I'll align harmonically at the 3+3 compound beat: beat1=Bb (3 eighths), beat2=Eb at G/2 with Cm7 passing.

            MEASURE LAYOUT (6 eighths per bar):
            Pickup: F4 (1 eighth) — Bb (I)
            M1: d(2e) A/2(1e) c/2(1e) B/2(1e) G/2(1e) — Bb → Cm7 → Eb
            M2: F(2e) G/2(1e) F(2e) F/2(1e) — Bb → F → Bb
            M3: G/2(1e) A/2(1e) B/2(1e) B/2(1e) c/2(1e) d/2(1e) — Eb → E° → C
            M4: c(2e) c(2e) F/2(1e) c(?) — wait: c3/2(3e) c(2e) F/2(1e) = 6e ✓ — F (I/V)
            M5: d(2e) A/2(1e) c/2(1e) B/2(1e) G/2(1e) — Bb → Cm7 → Eb
            M6: F(2e) G/2(1e) F(2e) F/2(1e) — Bb → F → Bb
            M7: G(2e+? wait: G(2e) G/2(1e) A/2(1e) G/2(1e) F/2(1e) = 6e) — Eb → Cm → F7 → F
            M8: B3/2(3e) B(2e) d/2(1e) — Bb (I, strong)
            M9: d(2e) D/2(1e) D/2(1e) =E/2(1e) ^F/2(1e) — D7
            M10: G(2e) A/2(1e) B(2e) d/2(1e) — Gm → D → Gm
            M11: c/2(1e) B/2(1e) A/2(1e) G/2(1e) A/2(1e) G/2(1e) — C7 → F
            M12: F3/2(3e) F(2e) F/2(1e) — F (V of Bb)
            M13: d(2e) A/2(1e) c/2(1e) B/2(1e) G/2(1e) — Bb → Cm7 → Eb
            M14: F(2e) G/2(1e) F(2e) F/2(1e) — Bb → F → Bb
            M15: G(2e) G/2(1e) A/2(1e) G/2(1e) F/2(1e) — Eb → Cm → F7 → F
            M16: B3/2(3e) B(2e) — Bb (whole bar, 5 eighths? — B3/2 = 3e, B = 2e → 5e??)
            Actually the ABC says "^Bb"B3/2 B| — in L:1/4, B3/2 = dotted quarter (3/2 L units = 3 eighths), B = quarter (2 eighths) = 5 eighths total, not 6
            This is a truncated final bar? or the source has it as 5/8? Let me treat as 5-eighth final bar.
            Actually it may be that the "^Bb" pickup from bar 16 means bar 16 = 5 eighths (full bar minus 1 pickup eighth). That makes sense: pickup = 1 eighth, final bar = 5 eighths (completes the hypermeasure). So total across pickup+final = 6.
          -->
          <scoreDef meter.count="6" meter.unit="8" key.sig="2f">
            <staffGrp symbol="bracket" barthru="true">
              <staffDef n="1" lines="5" clef.shape="G" clef.line="2" label="Melody">
                <keySig sig="2f" />
              </staffDef>
              <staffGrp symbol="brace">
                <staffDef n="2" lines="5" clef.shape="G" clef.line="2" label="RH">
                  <keySig sig="2f" />
                </staffDef>
                <staffDef n="3" lines="5" clef.shape="F" clef.line="4" label="LH">
                  <keySig sig="2f" />
                </staffDef>
              </staffGrp>
            </staffGrp>
          </scoreDef>
          <section>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- PICKUP: 1 eighth. Bb (I). Gentle opening single note -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="0" type="pickup" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="p1s1n1" dur="8" oct="4" pname="f" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- RH: F4 single (anticipation) -->
                  <note xml:id="p1s2n1" dur="8" oct="4" pname="f" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- LH: Bb2-F3 (I open 5th) -->
                  <chord xml:id="p1s3c1" dur="8">
                    <note xml:id="p1s3n1" pname="b" oct="2" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="p1s3n2" pname="f" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">①</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M1: 6 eighths. Bb/Cm7/Eb. Melody: d(4) A/2 c/2 B/2 G/2 -->
            <!-- tstamp 1=beat1(dotted-qtr), tstamp 4=beat2(second dotted-qtr) -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="1" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- d = quarter (2 eighths) -->
                  <note xml:id="m1s1n1" dur="4" oct="5" pname="d" />
                  <!-- A/2 = eighth -->
                  <note xml:id="m1s1n2" dur="8" oct="4" pname="a" />
                  <!-- c/2 = eighth -->
                  <note xml:id="m1s1n3" dur="8" oct="5" pname="c" />
                  <!-- B/2 = eighth -->
                  <note xml:id="m1s1n4" dur="8" oct="4" pname="b" accid.ges="f" />
                  <!-- G/2 = eighth (Eb chord note) -->
                  <note xml:id="m1s1n5" dur="8" oct="4" pname="g" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat 1 (dotted quarter): Bb4-D5 (I "33") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n1" pname="b" oct="4" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n2" pname="d" oct="5" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat 2 first 2 eighths: C5-Eb5 (ii7 inner) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s2c2" dur="4">
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n3" pname="c" oct="5" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n4" pname="e" oct="5" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat 2 last eighth: G4-Bb4 (IV passing) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s2c3" dur="8">
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n5" pname="g" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s2n6" pname="b" oct="4" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat 1: Bb2-F3-Bb3-D4 (I "334") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n1" pname="b" oct="2" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n2" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n3" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n4" pname="d" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat 2: C3-G3-Eb3 (ii7 "333") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s3c2" dur="4">
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n5" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n6" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n7" pname="g" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Pickup to Eb: Eb3-Bb3 (IV open) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m1s3c3" dur="8">
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n8" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m1s3n9" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">①</harm>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="4">②m7</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M2: 6 eighths. Bb/F/Bb. Melody: F(4) G/2 F(4) F/2 -->
            <!-- F=quarter(2e), G/2=eighth(1e), F=quarter(2e), F/2=eighth(1e) = 6e ✓ -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="2" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="m2s1n1" dur="4" oct="4" pname="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m2s1n2" dur="8" oct="4" pname="g" />
                  <note xml:id="m2s1n3" dur="4" oct="4" pname="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m2s1n4" dur="8" oct="4" pname="f" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat1: F4-A4 (I 2nd inv "34") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m2s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m2s2n1" pname="f" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s2n2" pname="a" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat2: C4-F4 (V sus4 "42") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m2s2c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m2s2n3" pname="c" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s2n4" pname="f" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat1: Bb2-F3-Bb3 (I "334") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m2s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n1" pname="b" oct="2" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n2" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n3" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat2: F2-C3-F3-A3 (V root pos open) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m2s3c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n4" pname="f" oct="2" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n5" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n6" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m2s3n7" pname="a" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">①</harm>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="4">⑤</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M3: 6 eighths. Eb/E°/C. Melody: G/2 A/2 B/2 B/2 c/2 d/2 -->
            <!-- Ascending passing line. E° = vii° in Bb (A C Eb). C = nondiatonic → ③m(Cm) -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="3" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n1" dur="8" oct="4" pname="g" />
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n2" dur="8" oct="4" pname="a" />
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n3" dur="8" oct="4" pname="b" accid.ges="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n4" dur="8" oct="4" pname="b" accid.ges="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n5" dur="8" oct="5" pname="c" />
                  <note xml:id="m3s1n6" dur="8" oct="5" pname="d" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat1: G4-Bb4 (IV "43" 1st inv — Eb chord starts on G) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m3s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m3s2n1" pname="g" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s2n2" pname="b" oct="4" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat2: A4-C5 (vii° "33", then → Cm) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m3s2c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m3s2n3" pname="a" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s2n4" pname="c" oct="5" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Beat1: Eb3-Bb3-G3 (IV root "33") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m3s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n1" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n2" pname="g" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n3" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- Beat2: C3-G3-Eb3-A3 (iii "333" open) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m3s3c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n4" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n5" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n6" pname="g" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m3s3n7" pname="a" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">④</harm>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="4">③m</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M4: 6 eighths. F(V). Melody: c3/2 c F/2 -->
            <!-- c3/2 = dotted-quarter (3e), c = quarter (2e), F/2 = eighth (1e) = 6 ✓ -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="4" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="m4s1n1" dur="4" dots="1" oct="5" pname="c" />
                  <note xml:id="m4s1n2" dur="4" oct="5" pname="c" />
                  <note xml:id="m4s1n3" dur="8" oct="4" pname="f" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- Full bar V: C4-A4 (V "34" 2nd inv, open) -->
                  <chord xml:id="m4s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m4s2n1" pname="c" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s2n2" pname="a" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- beat2: F4-A4 resolving to I approach -->
                  <chord xml:id="m4s2c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m4s2n3" pname="f" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s2n4" pname="a" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <!-- beat1: F2-C3-A3 (V "34") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m4s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n1" pname="f" oct="2" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n2" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n3" pname="a" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                  <!-- beat2: F2-C3-F3-A3 (V root "334") -->
                  <chord xml:id="m4s3c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n4" pname="f" oct="2" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n5" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n6" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m4s3n7" pname="a" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">⑤</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M5: repeat of M1 (Bb/Cm7/Eb). Melody: d A/2 c/2 B/2 G/2 -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="5" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="m5s1n1" dur="4" oct="5" pname="d" />
                  <note xml:id="m5s1n2" dur="8" oct="4" pname="a" />
                  <note xml:id="m5s1n3" dur="8" oct="5" pname="c" />
                  <note xml:id="m5s1n4" dur="8" oct="4" pname="b" accid.ges="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m5s1n5" dur="8" oct="4" pname="g" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <chord xml:id="m5s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n1" pname="b" oct="4" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n2" pname="d" oct="5" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m5s2c2" dur="4">
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n3" pname="c" oct="5" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n4" pname="e" oct="5" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m5s2c3" dur="8">
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n5" pname="g" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s2n6" pname="b" oct="4" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <chord xml:id="m5s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n1" pname="b" oct="2" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n2" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n3" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n4" pname="d" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m5s3c2" dur="4">
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n5" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n6" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n7" pname="g" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m5s3c3" dur="8">
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n8" pname="e" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m5s3n9" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="1">①</harm>
              <harm staff="1" tstamp="4">②m7</harm>
            </measure>

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- M6: repeat of M2. Bb/F/Bb. Melody: F G/2 F F/2 -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <measure n="6" right="single">
              <staff n="1">
                <layer n="1">
                  <note xml:id="m6s1n1" dur="4" oct="4" pname="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m6s1n2" dur="8" oct="4" pname="g" />
                  <note xml:id="m6s1n3" dur="4" oct="4" pname="f" />
                  <note xml:id="m6s1n4" dur="8" oct="4" pname="f" />
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="2">
                <layer n="1">
                  <chord xml:id="m6s2c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m6s2n1" pname="f" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s2n2" pname="d" oct="5" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m6s2c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m6s2n3" pname="c" oct="4" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s2n4" pname="a" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
              </staff>
              <staff n="3">
                <layer n="1">
                  <chord xml:id="m6s3c1" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n1" pname="b" oct="2" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n2" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n3" pname="b" oct="3" accid.ges="f" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n4" pname="d" oct="4" />
                  </chord>
                  <chord xml:id="m6s3c2" dur="4" dots="1">
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n5" pname="f" oct="2" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n6" pname="c" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n7" pname="f" oct="3" />
                    <note xml:id="m6s3n8" pname="a" oct="3" />
                  </chord>
                </layer>
